        "ggGkzemG1js_text": "<span style=\"color:#055BDC;\"><strong>You're One Step Away From Lasting At-Home Relief You Can Feel.</strong></span>",
        "ggWQIG9fsLw_text": "Why Your Sciatica Keeps Coming Back (And Why Pills &amp; Appointments Never Fix It)",
        "ggN5O792d2I_youtubeUrl": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cyzh48XRS4M",
        "ggN5O792d2I_vimeoUrl": "https://vimeo.com/347119375",
        "ggN5O792d2I_html5Url": "https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/598d5746026d49adada2d60864a5715a.mp4",
        "ggN5O792d2I_poster_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/Sciatica_Keeps_Coming.webp",
        "ggymlr3ksYA_text": "Why Your Sciatica Keeps Coming Back (And Why Pills &amp; Appointments Never Fix It)",
        "ggj3LHKR5Jp_text": "<p>Most sciatica treatments fail because they only mask symptoms. Pills fade, appointments don’t last, and surgery is risky. The real cause is nerve compression and muscle shutdown in the lower back. When your discs collapse, they pinch the sciatic nerve, block muscle activation, and trap you in a cycle of pain, stiffness, and weakness.</p>",
        "gg4YoJ0BCta_text": "<p>The only way out? Relieve the pressure, restore blood flow, and reactivate the muscles that support your spine.</p>"
      }
    },
    "gp_section_597882213446779788": {
      "type": "gp-section-597882213446779788",
      "settings": {
        "section_preload": "false",
        "checksum": "25ce3fa7191a246406feadc398236a7f8ca5b669ec091061ce42819081a6ce9f_1_1_1_0__1",
        "ggzRfc3KmKh_text": "One Belt. Three Therapies. Total Back Relief at Home.",
        "gg4GNxuDqa0_youtubeUrl": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cyzh48XRS4M",
