        "gg4GNxuDqa0_html5Url": "https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/ebefa6da57c146a3ab43b58e99b5fdaf.mp4",
        "gg4GNxuDqa0_poster_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/One_Belt..webp",
        "ggclZmxOds__text": "One Belt. Three Therapies. Total Back Relief at Home.",
        "gg5gEyQLqLG_text": "<p>That’s exactly what the SmoothSpine Red Light Therapy Belt was designed to do.</p>",
        "gg-RifOCijk_text": "<p>It’s the only at-home device that blends:</p>",
        "ggu6Yd3u6Yx_text": "<p><strong>Infrared &amp; Red Light Therapy (660nm + 850nm) </strong>— to calm inflammation and restore tissue health</p>",
        "ggyZ6Gf5lWo_text": "<p><strong>Soothing Heat </strong>— to melt stiffness and loosen tight muscles</p>",
        "ggrYT7cGWvp_text": "<p><strong>Vibration Massage </strong>— to stimulate circulation and reawaken dormant back muscles</p>",
        "gglNkdnoYHM_text": "<p>Together, these therapies create a complete healing environment — so your back can finally recover while you relax at home.</p>"
      }
    },
