    "gp_section_597882213447369612": {
      "type": "gp-section-597882213447369612",
      "settings": {
        "section_preload": "false",
        "checksum": "1ba286a8cab59d181ee5b9bdbdc6e8a581cd4db4b5768bc341b452c74c0b58d4_1_1_1_0__1",
        "ggrydDXALPH_text": "Real Users, Real Life-Changing Results",
        "gg_nv0E1WSj_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/1758119542121_Screenshot_2_1.webp",
        "gg029TQ7PQT_text": "<p>“I Didn’t Think Anything Could Replace My Heating Pad”</p>",
        "ggnkoHZd9S5_text": "<p>\"I’ve been using heating pads for years, and while they felt good in the moment, the pain always came back the second I stood up. I didn’t believe anything portable could go deeper. But after two weeks with the SmoothSpine Therapy Belt, I can honestly say it’s night and day. The combination of heat, vibration, and light therapy gives lasting relief. I finally wake up without stiffness.\"</p>",
        "ggmciU_MO8m_text": "<p>— Jennifer S.</p>",
        "ggx_FgcD6ei_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/1758119553841_Screenshot_1_1.webp",
        "ggBi7vQvbIj_text": "<p>“I Was Skeptical About Another ‘At-Home Gadget’”</p>",
        "ggJ8hCrLXJq_text": "<p>\"When you’ve tried chiropractors, physical therapy, and endless gadgets, it’s hard to believe one more thing will work. I almost didn’t order this belt, but I’m glad I did. The compression plus red light therapy eased the stabbing pain down my leg within a week. By the second week, I could cook dinner and walk my dog without wincing. This isn’t a gimmick — it’s real relief.\"</p>",
        "ggReBUA1njy_text": "<p>— Mark D.</p>",
        "ggcIBXq5yW6_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/1758119578101_Screenshot_3_1.webp",
        "gg4lOxj8MET_text": "<p>“I Was Afraid of Needing Surgery”</p>",
        "ggZSVoxxXVa_text": "<p>\"My doctor was already bringing up surgery for my sciatica, and that terrified me. I needed something safe to try first. A friend recommended the SmoothSpine Therapy Belt, and it changed everything. The first session gave me a sense of release I’d never felt before, and within a month, my daily pain went from an 8 to a 2. I’m moving again — no surgery needed.\"</p>",
        "ggQgcHb_VvV_text": "<p>— Linda K.</p>"
      }
    },
