    "gp_section_597882213447238540": {
      "type": "gp-section-597882213447238540",
      "settings": {
        "section_preload": "false",
        "checksum": "2f90b750c5759fa3d7ec25877e5b56f7c59ad65a422aef6562d7d015f7270a81_1_1_1_0__1",
        "ggBJa8Yn5GB_text": "Frequently Asked Questions",
        "gg_vblMSRbJ_childItem_0": "<p>Is this safe to use at home?</p>",
        "gg_vblMSRbJ_childItem_1": "<p>Will it actually work if I’ve had pain for years?</p>",
        "gg_vblMSRbJ_childItem_2": "<p>How soon can I feel results?</p>",
        "gg_vblMSRbJ_childItem_3": "<p>Is it complicated to set up?</p>",
        "gg_vblMSRbJ_childItem_4": "<p>Can I use it if I’m not flexible or have limited mobility?</p>",
        "gg_vblMSRbJ_childItem_5": "<p>What if it doesn’t work for me?</p>",
        "ggJ59b-ywE__text": "<p>Yes! The SmoothSpine Therapy Belt uses the same clinically proven therapies used by physiotherapists, but at safe, adjustable levels for home use. Everything is non-invasive, drug-free, and designed to work gently with your body.</p>",
        "ggOF78_pLax_text": "<p>Many of our customers struggled with sciatica and back pain for 5, 10, even 20 years before finding relief with the belt. By addressing the root cause — nerve compression and muscle shutdown — the therapies work regardless of how long you’ve been suffering.</p>",
        "ggGBgdMGN1b_text": "<p>Some people notice relief after the very first session. Most report feeling lighter, looser, and less stiff within the first week, with major improvements showing by the 2–3 week mark when used consistently for 15 minutes a day.</p>",
        "gg5779-Q2LD_text": "<p>Not at all! Just strap it comfortably around your lower back, choose your mode, and press start. The adjustable fit works for all body types, and the simple controls make it easy to relax while the belt does the work.</p>",
        "ggrcqOh_tmz_text": "<p>Absolutely. You don’t need to do any special exercises or positions. The belt does the heavy lifting — decompressing your spine, restoring blood flow, and reactivating muscles — all while you’re sitting, lying down, or even lightly moving around the house.</p>",
        "ggZ3I5t3Bhg_text": "<p>You’re fully covered by our 90-day money-back guarantee. Try the SmoothSpine Therapy Belt daily for three months. If you don’t feel a noticeable difference, simply send it back for a full refund — no questions asked.</p>"
      }
    },
